dataItem.label: % Utilization
dataItem.name: % Utilization
dataItem.expression: case when (case when [Budget Amount] is missing then 0 else [Budget Amount] end)=0 then 0 else ( (case when [Approved Amount] is missing then 0 else [Approved Amount] end + case when [Pending Amount] is missing then 0 else [Pending Amount] end)/ case when [Budget Amount] is missing then 0 else [Budget Amount] end) end

dataItem.name: Units
dataItem.expression: total([InvoiceMatterOrg].[Fee Total Submitted Units] for [Organization Name],[Matter Type])

dataItem.name: Gross Amount
dataItem.expression: total([InvoiceMatterOrg].[User Fee Total Gross Amount] for [Organization Name],[Matter Type])

dataItem.label: Blended Rate
dataItem.name: Blended Rate
dataItem.expression: case when (case when [Units] is missing then 0 else [Units] end) = 0 then 0 else ([Gross Amount]/[Units]) end

dataItem.name: Report Utilization
dataItem.expression: case when (case when total([Budget Amount] for report) is missing then 0 else total([Budget Amount] for report) end)=0 then 0 else ( (case when total([Approved Amount] for report) is missing then 0 else total([Approved Amount] for report) end + case when total([Pending Amount] for report) is missing then 0 else total([Pending Amount] for report) end)/ case when total([Budget Amount] for report) is missing then 0 else total([Budget Amount] for report) end) end

dataItem.name: Report Blended Rate
dataItem.expression: case when (case when total([Units] for report) is missing then 0 else total( [Units] for report) end) = 0 then 0 else (total([Gross Amount] for report)/total([Units] for report)) end

dataItem.label: % Utilization
dataItem.name: Org Utilization
dataItem.expression: case when (case when total([Budget Amount] for [Organization Name]) is missing then 0 else total([Budget Amount] for [Organization Name]) end)=0 then 0 else ( (case when total([Approved Amount] for [Organization Name]) is missing then 0 else total([Approved Amount] for [Organization Name]) end + case when total([Pending Amount] for [Organization Name]) is missing then 0 else total([Pending Amount] for [Organization Name]) end)/ case when total([Budget Amount] for [Organization Name]) is missing then 0 else total([Budget Amount] for [Organization Name]) end) end

dataItem.label: Approved Amount
dataItem.name: Approved Amount
dataItem.expression: total([BudgetMatterOrg].[User Approved Amount] for [Organization Name],[Matter Type])

dataItem.name: Pending Amount
dataItem.expression: total([BudgetMatterOrg].[User Pending Amount] for [Organization Name],[Matter Type])

dataItem.label: Spend Amount
dataItem.name: Spend Amount
dataItem.expression: case when [MainQuery].[Org Approved Amount] is missing then 0 else [MainQuery].[Org Approved Amount] end + case when [MainQuery].[Org Pending Amount] is missing then 0 else [MainQuery].[Org Pending Amount] end

dataItem.label: Utilization
dataItem.name: Org Utilization
dataItem.expression: case when (case when [Org Budget Amount] is missing then 0 else [Org Budget Amount] end)=0 then 0 else ( (case when [Spend Amount] is missing then 0 else [Spend Amount] end)/ case when [Org Budget Amount] is missing then 0 else [Org Budget Amount] end) end

dataItem.label: Net Amount
dataItem.name: Net Amount
dataItem.expression: case when [Business View].[FACTINVOICEHEADER].[User Total Net Amount] is null then 0 else [Business View].[FACTINVOICEHEADER].[User Total Net Amount]end

dataItem.name: User Fee Total Gross Amount
dataItem.expression: case when [Business View].[FACTINVOICEHEADER].[User Fee Total Gross Amount]is missing then 0 else [Business View].[FACTINVOICEHEADER].[User Fee Total Gross Amount] end

dataItem.name: Fee Total Submitted Units
dataItem.expression: case when [Business View].[FACTINVOICEHEADER].[FEE_TOTAL_SUBMITTED_UNITS] is missing then 0 else [Business View].[FACTINVOICEHEADER].[FEE_TOTAL_SUBMITTED_UNITS] end
